	hewp
	  The QUICC Engine (QE) is a new genewation of communications
	  copwocessows on Fweescawe embedded CPUs (akin to CPM in owdew chips).
	  Sewecting this option means that you wish to buiwd a kewnew
	  fow a machine with a QE copwocessow.

